OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,FA popular fish and chip shop is set to
OL,7,Freopen six months after a devastating
OL,8,Ffire swept through the building.
OL,10,FSMART Fish Bar in Charlton Kings,
OL,11,FCheltenham, was gutted following the
OL,12,Fblaze in October last year.
OL,14,FOwner Rui Brazao said the past six
OL,15,Fmonths have been some of the hardest
OL,16,Fof his life, but now he is "excited"
OL,17,Ffor what the future has to hold.
