OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,FHe said they have been working seven
OL,7,Fdays a week "to make sure everything
OL,8,Fis perfect for the reopening," and
OL,9,Fthanked the community for their
OL,10,Fsupport after the fire.
OL,12,FMr Brazao said he was finishing off a
OL,13,Flarge order of around 100 fish and
OL,14,Fchips, when he noticed flames coming
OL,15,Fout of the frying range on 12 October
OL,16,F2023.
