OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,FHe recalled: "Within about two to
OL,7,Fthree minutes, the whole place was
OL,8,Ffull of smoke. The fire service
OL,9,Farrived pretty quickly and managed to
OL,10,Fput it out, but it left such a mess.
OL,12,F"It was just such a shock," Mr Brazao
OL,13,Fadded. "I was just looking at
OL,14,Feverything thinking right, how do we
OL,15,Fget around this?"
OL,17,FWork to rebuild the shop started
OL,18,Fstraight away, and now a new state-of-
OL,19,Fthe-art kitchen has been installed
OL,20,Fwhich aims to prevent future fires and
OL,21,Fmake the business more efficient.
