OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,F"It was a lot of work," Mr Brazao
OL,7,Fsaid. "We're talking about repairs
OL,8,Ffrom top to bottom of the shop - a new
OL,9,Frange, a new ceiling, new walls."
OL,11,FMr Brazao said he was a "coin-flip
OL,12,Faway from not being able to reopen the
OL,13,Fshop" due to the cost of the
OL,14,Frenovation, and there were points when
OL,15,Fhe "almost threw the towel in and
OL,16,Fcalled it a day."
