OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,F"We couldn't figure out how to make it
OL,7,Fwork financially," he explained. "But
OL,8,Fthanks to the support of the local
OL,9,Fcommunity and local companies, we've
OL,10,Fmanaged to make it work."
OL,12,F"The support from everyone has just
OL,13,Fbeen amazing," Mr Brazao added.
OL,15,FHe said customers have been in touch
OL,16,Ffrom all over the world saying that
OL,17,Fthey're sorry for what happened and
OL,18,Fsending messages of encouragement.
