OL,3,CPopular fish and chip shop to reopen
OL,4,Cafter catastrophic fire
OL,6,F"I've had people from America
OL,7,Fmessaging me saying that they can't
OL,8,Fwait to come back for their fish and
OL,9,Fchips," he explained. "The support has
OL,10,Fjust been absurd."
OL,12,FMr Brazao said is happy to be back and
OL,13,Fis now planning to expand the business
OL,14,Fby taking on online orders.
OL,16,F"We think we're good enough to compete
OL,17,Fwith anyone in town," he said. "And I
OL,18,Fthink the people on the other side of
OL,19,Ftown are missing out on some fantastic
OL,20,Ffish and chips."
